name: 杰克·帕里-琼斯
name_full: 杰克·帕里-琼斯 Jack Parry-Jones
birth_place: 英国南威尔士梅瑟蒂德菲尔
introduction: Jack Parry-Jones is a Welsh actor known for House of the Dragon (2024), Hijack (2023) and The Crown (2019). In 2017, Jack won multiple awards for his leading role in the independent film and festival favorite, Moon Dogs. This included winning a BAFTA Cymru Best Actor Award and a Jury Award for Best Actor at Newport Beach Film Festival.
